snippet.title: Super Monkey Ball: Banana Blitz HD | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Jump, tilt, and roll back into Super Monkey Ball: Banana Blitz HD when it launches on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch on October 29, 2019, with a Steam release in Winter 2019!
 
Get your first look at all the HD rolling action in our new gameplay trailer!

http://bit.ly/SMBBlitzHD
